Items.Title: A Local Law to amend the administrative code of the city of New York, in relation to information distribution and annual reporting with respect to the availability and utilization of clinical preventive medical services provided to city employees, retirees and covered family members by health maintenance organizations, health insurance companies and medicare plan providers under contract with the city of New York to provide health insurance coverage to such employees, retirees and covered family members.
Items.MatterName: Availability and utilization of clinical preventive medical services.
